snippet.title: Gimmick in the Chaos Dimension - Music Demo
snippet.description:
Demonstration video of the intro cutscene, title music, menu music, and some level themes. Watch carefully and there's a steam achievement in there, too.
Gimmick in the Chaos Dimension launches May 31!
